User Stories - Requirements - Features

## ADMIN USER - Manage Users

- [] **Users list**: Dynamic list of users to manage.
- [] **Filter users**: Filter by email or username.
- [] **Change roles**: Promote unsigned → regular or admin.
- [] **Block users**: Temporarily suspend or block users for bad behavior.
- [] **Unblock users**: Restore access for previously blocked users.

## ADMIN USER - Manage Categories

- [] **Categories list**: Dynamic categories management.
- [] **Add category**: Admin can add categories.
- [] **Delete category**: Admin can delete categories.

## ADMIN USER - Settings of the Notifications

- [ ] **Notification options**: Configure types and delivery.
- [ ] **Notification types**: daily content, comment on photo, favorite album update, profile viewed.

## ALL USERS - Authentication

- [X] **Login page**: Sign in with email and password.
- [X] **Register page**: Sign up with username, email and password.
- [X] **Sign out**: End session.
- [X] **Navigate auth**: Switch between login and register windows.
- [X] **Access control**: Restrict features to authenticated users (regular roles).
- [X] **Blocked account notice**: Show suspension notice and contact admin option.
- [ ] **Unsigned user limits**: Allow browsing but with limited interactions (e.g., view-only top photos).

## ADMIN USER - Profile

- [] **Contacts**: Can view contact messages sent by users and mark them as resolved.
- [] **Reporting**: View reports of inappropriate content and take action (e.g., remove content, block user).

## ALL USERS - Profile

- [ ] **Avatar**: Users have avatars and can update them. (accept jpg/png, max 2MB)
- [ ] **Change password**: User can change account password.
- [ ] **Albums**: Create and manage photo albums.
- [ ] **List albums**: Show user's albums and favorite albums.
- [ ] **Edit album**: Rename and delete own albums.
- [ ] **Delete content**: Users can delete only their own photos.
- [ ] **Add photo to Album**: Upload photo with short description (max 150 chars), publish date, category, and image file

## ALL USERS - Photo Content & Albums (Catalog - Explore)

- [ ] **Gallery**: Display a gallery of photos (catalog - Explore)
- [ ] **Photo Preview Card**: Show selected photo with preview details (author(avatar, username), nlikes, nComments, rating)
- [ ] **Buttons on photo preview**: Add Like, View details, View comments, View album, Rate photo and Report photo buttons on photo preview.
- [ ] **Photo Detail View**: Show full photo with metadata and interactions:
  - nlikes, nComments, author, like button, view comments, view album, rate photo and report photo buttons on photo detail view, publish date, category, description. 
- **Comments View**: Show all comments with Scrollable list of comments and the photo preview! Each comment should display the commenter's avatar, username, comment text, and publish date.
- **Album View**: Show all photos in the album with album details (album name, author, category), and interactions (navigate photos preview, like photos, view commnents, rate photos, report photos, add album to favorites).
- **Rating**: Allow users to rate photos (1-5 stars) and show average rating on photo preview and detail view.
  - Will display a small tkinter scalle for non photos rated for logged users, and the average rating for photos with ratings. Users can only rate a photo once! Will have a rating icon like ⭐ 4.5 and also aside the system scale tkinter ⭐ 4.5 (average rating) and ⭐ (user rating with the tkk.Scale) on the photo preview and detail view.

## ALL USERS - Filtering & Sorting (Catalog - Explore)

- [ ] **Filter by user**: Search photos by author.
- [ ] **Filter by category**: Select category filter.
- [ ] **Sort by views/likes/date/rate**: Allow sorting catalog by popularity or recency.
  - Default sorting should be by publish date (newest first).
  - Sorting options should include: "Most Recent", "Most Viewed", "Most Liked", "Highest Rated".

## ALL USERS - Interaction (Catalog - Explore)

- [ ] **Comments**: Users can comment and see comments on photos.
- [ ] **Likes**: Users can like photos.
- [ ] **Rating**: Users can rate photos (1-5 stars) and see average rating.
- [ ] **Reporting**: Users can report inappropriate photos or comments, providing a reason for the report ( e.g., "Inappropriate content", "Spam", "Harassment"). Reported content should be flagged for admin review.
- [ ] **Favorites**: Users can add albums to favorites.

## ALL USERS - Notifications

- [ ] **Notifications**: Notify owners on comments/likes and users for followed categories.

## ALL USERS - Reporting & Moderation

- [X] **Contact Admin**: Blocked users can contact admin to resolve issues.
- [ ] **Report content**: Users can report inappropriate photos or comments, providing a reason for the report ( e.g., "Inappropriate content", "Spam", "Harassment"). Reported content should be flagged for admin review.

## ADMIN DASHBOARD & DATA

- [ ] **Dashboard**: Totals (photos, photos by category, users, pending approvals).
- [ ] **Manage reported content**: Admin can review and remove inappropriate photos/comments.
